name: NPS_Reinforced_Fan-back_Polyfold_Chairs_(Pack_of_12)
reviews: I was pleasantly surprised when I unpacked these chairs. They were better than I even hoped they would be. Very comfortable for a folding chair. The seat has a little sculpting to it - not perfectly flat - and that helps to make it comfortable. I bought them to have for meetings and events in my home and they are perfect. Purchase these chairs with confidence. They are lovely.
Loved the large quantity. Looks great. The high weight capacity is good, also.
description: A comfortable design and a fan back make this polyfold folding chair uniqueThis folding chair is perfect for indoor and outdoor spaces Color options: Blue, rose, black, white High-radius fan back provides added ergonomic comfort and breathability Polypropylene plastic seat and back Contoured for stacking up to 80 inches high (26 chairs) Plastic will not fade or rust Features a powder-coated steel frame for added strength Reinforced with 0.875-inch round tubing Two U-shaped cross braces Three rivets on either side Double hinges Each chair measures 34.5 inches high x 18.5 inches wide x 20.75 inches deepPack of 12 chairsMaterialPlasticSet SizeSet of 12Chair Back HeightHigh BackColorBlack, Pink, WhiteFurniture Frame MaterialPlasticFurniture PatternSolidSeat StyleUpholstered
